# bhcom-ba (Angular 21)

Logistics SPA with **employee** (`/`) and **admin** (`/admin`) portals. Prefer existing abstractions over new UI frameworks.

## Commands

- `npm start` — dev server (4200)
- `npm run build` — production build
- `npm test` — run existing Vitest suite only when asked; see **Testing** below

## Testing (agents)

- **Never add unit tests** — no new `*.spec.ts` files, Vitest cases, test helpers, or test-only dependencies.
- Do not scaffold, suggest, or include unit tests as part of feature work, refactors, or bug fixes unless the user explicitly requests tests.
- Do not extend or rewrite existing unit tests unless the user explicitly asks.
- Prefer manual verification (`npm start`, `npm run build`) over adding coverage.

## Source map (read files when implementing, don’t guess)

- Root routes: `src/app/app.routes.ts` (login + lazy portal trees)
- Portal routes: `src/app/routes/employee.routes.ts`, `admin.routes.ts`
- Auth: `src/app/core/auth/`
- Portal config/guards: `src/app/core/portal/` (`PORTAL_CONFIG`, `portalMatchGuard`, `guestGuard`)
- App shell: `src/app/layout/` — `app-shell`, `sidebar`, `topbar`
- Sidebar nav: `employee-nav.config.ts`, `admin-nav.config.ts` (types in `nav.model.ts`)
- Layout services: `src/app/core/layout/sidebar.service.ts`, `theme/`, `i18n/`
- Forms framework: `src/app/features/shared/form/` — barrel `index.ts`
- Tables framework: `src/app/features/shared/table/` — barrel `index.ts`
- Features: `features/employee/`, `features/admin/`, `features/shared/`
- i18n: `public/assets/en.json` + `bh.json` (`portal.*`, `login.*`, `nav.admin.*`)
- Theme: `src/styles.scss`; breakpoints: `src/styles/_breakpoints.scss`, `core/layout/viewport.ts`

## Layout behavior (do not reimplement ad hoc)

- **Desktop:** persistent sidebar (`SidebarService.collapsed`), panel collapse/expand in brand row.
- **Mobile (≤768px):** topbar hamburger → drawer; brand shows portal suffix + close (X).
- **Main scroll:** `.app-shell__content` only.

## References for patterns

- Form page: `features/employee/fleet/vehicles/create-vehicle-page.*` + `create-vehicle.form.ts`
- Stepper: `features/employee/shipments/create-shipment/`
- Table page: `features/employee/shipments/shipments-page.*` + `shipment.table.ts`
